description:
Вне времени, suspended in a vacuum, the island continues its endless journey. The moon illuminates the glass surface of the frozen lake, which holds its history. The island continues to live, despite the monstrous frosts and the distances it overcomes, while its inhabitants believe that they found themselves on it not by chance. 


Guiding stars will definitely lead it where it should be ;^)
